Delek Group Talking to HSBC, Barclays on Tamar, Calcalist Says

-- B y   S h o s h a n n a   S o l o m o n
-- 
2011-10-02T06:40:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-02/delek-group-talking-to-hsbc-barclays-on-tamar-calcalist-says.html
Delek Group Ltd. (DLEKG)  is in talks with
 HSBC Holdings Plc (HSBA)  and  Barclays Plc (BARC)  for a loan of about 1 billion
shekels to refinance Tamar gas field debt and finance new
equipment for Tamar, Calcalist reported, without saying where it
got the information.  A spokesman for Delek declined to comment, when contacted
by Bloomberg News today.   To contact the reporter on this story:
Shoshanna Solomon in Tel Aviv at 
 ssolomon22@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Claudia Maedler at 
 cmaedler@bloomberg.net  